{"tid":1593321,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"午夜的連儂牆 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-09-25T04:22:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T04:26:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"72beb0e6bd23eebcbc40dd098b4beefbf28633d7","tid":1593321,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:22:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20190925/20774353\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190925%2F20774353&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9ARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=b2d2e9de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190925%2F20774353&h=0d11175f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20190925/20774353</a><br />\n<br />\n午夜的連儂牆 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190925/large/1569306404_c23e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190925%2Flarge%2F1569306404_c23e.jpg&h=63bf701f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何妖枉作小人兼淆底，其策動的「香港清潔隊」，騎呢又hea做，一群鄉音大叔大媽撕毀多處連儂牆，製造垃圾，且烏合之眾不專業，收錢卻吞卟，超過一人高度的貼紙全然不理。<br />\n<br />\n即使9.21拆、撕、砸、鏟，當晚不少連儂牆已經重整，統統換上10.1全民黑衫日國殤日之類，過氣的就過去了。<br />\n<br />\n各區小朋友開夜工，有男有女，但女的心思細密，她們已投入「感情」，依依不捨，要苦勸才放棄深夜死守。現在想通了，舊的不去新的不來，人生就是這樣。<br />\n<br />\n走過家居附近地鐵站的連儂牆，午夜11、12點，仍有三個十多廿歲的女生努力貼，我有點擔心藍絲和警察會無故騷擾，且黑警濫捕湊數，酷愛恰細路抓少女，所以我決定多待一陣有個照應。<br />\n<br />\n女孩有禮貌道謝，還說：「阿媽搞完兩機衫就嚟接我哋。」那麼我就等到有大人出現吧。不久，阿媽來了連阿爸也來了，這才放心──但百感交集，有些年輕人得到支持，有些與父母反目被打罵被趕逐，又窮又餓又無溫暖，仍堅持抗爭追求一個美好的香港，他們連明天身處何方是否頭破血流骨折受虐也不知道。走同樣的路，卻是不同的命，有些還死於非命&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我們真心感謝所有為逆權運動付出的年輕人！ <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n黃色物體 (林夕)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n中立者的報應 (馮睎乾)"},{"pid":"355263c884102c5d1d2e776dae69540a5992f63e","tid":1593321,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"fa306f47fd018b93d89294685be5c02ae7c8d0fc","tid":1593321,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:23:30.000Z","msg":"［請幫推行動post］今星期四：和你塞 美心MX<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590453</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O4KHbAX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO4KHbAX.jpg&h=3211b048&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"486a1846600814bfacecdd76f2ded9ac5929dbde","tid":1593321,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:26:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}